        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Weekly sync between Datagrid and GrowthX to discuss content performance and upcoming plans.](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=22.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [733 articles will be live by Saturday; performance metrics show positive trends](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=276.0)\n  - [New SOW and work streams in development, to be presented in coming weeks](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=283.0)\n  - [Content categories performing well: AI agents (real estate, finance), sales, insurance, automation](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=330.0)\n  - [LLM referrals at highs, with Perplexity increasing but ChatGPT still top referrer](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=348.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Content Production and Performance\n\n  - [733 articles scheduled to go live by Saturday](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=276.0)\n  - [No constraints or blockers in content production](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=280.0)\n  - [Overall performance increased compared to last week](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=305.0)\n  - [Uplift in organic channels and LLM-driven traffic](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=312.0)\n  - [Non-branded performance continues to increase](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=316.0)\n  - [Impressions at all-time high](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=319.0)\n  - [Now ranking in top spot for 176 non-branded keywords (30 more than last week)](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=322.0)\n  - [Best performing content categories:](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=330.0)\n    1.  New batch: AI agents for real estate and finance\n    2.  Older clusters: sales, insurance, and automation\n\n### LLM Referrals\n\n  - [LLM referrals at record highs](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=348.0)\n  - [Increase driven by growth in Perplexity referrals](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=348.0)\n  - [ChatGPT remains the top referrer among LLMs](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=348.0)\n\n### Upcoming Plans\n\n  - [New SOW (Statement of Work) and work streams in development](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=283.0)\n  - [Presentation of new plans expected in 1-2 weeks](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=288.0)\n  - [Mara out next week; team may present if ready, otherwise likely the following week](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=290.0)\n\n### Link Building and Thought Leadership\n\n  - [Continuing to post approved content](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=361.0)\n  - [Kaitlin has access to view current approvals](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=366.0)\n\n### Meeting Schedule\n\n  - [Future syncs canceled (reason not specified, possibly due to completed project phase)](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=366.0)\n\n### Conference Preparation (Toric)\n\n  - [Kaitlin dealing with booth submission deadline for upcoming conference](https://fathom.video/share/YibNYu5TmiLMCzRapbxqQmbTRsppqtBw?tab=summary&timestamp=78.0)\n  - [Struggling with floor